Title: Get CAN1 Config
Description: Get the initial or current values of the CAN1 configuration registers.

Title: Get CAN2 Config
Description: Get the initial or current values of the CAN2 configuration registers.

Title: Get CAN3 Config
Description: Get the initial or current values of the CAN3 configuration registers.

Title: Get CAN4 Config
Description: Get the initial or current values of the CAN4 configuration registers.

Title: Transmit CAN Message
Description: Transmits a CAN message using a specific message box.

Title: Get CAN Data
Description: Gets data from a received CAN message.

Title: Check TX Pending
Description: Checks to see if the Tx message box has a pending Tx request.

Title: Check RX Arrived
Description: Checks to see if the Rx message box has pending Rx data.

Title: Check Message Box Valid
Description: Checks to see if the message box is valid for operation.
